operation.expression: fn:concat('SELECT C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS ITEM_SKEY, C_BO_PRDCT_ALT_ID_XREF.PRDCT_ALT_ID AS ALTERNATE_PRODUCT_IDENTIFIER FROM ', $temp.temp_Schema ,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF , ' INNER JOIN ', $temp.temp_Schema,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_ALT_ID_XREF, ' ON ', $temp.temp_Schema ,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF,'.ROWID_XREF = ', $temp.temp_Schema,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_ALT_ID_XREF, '.PRDCT_MSTR_FK')

fn:concat('SELECT C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS ITEM_SKEY, C_BO_PRDCT_DSCR_XREF.LANG_KEY AS LANGUAGE, C_BO_PRDCT_DSCR_XREF.MTRL_DSCR AS PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM ', $temp.temp_Schema ,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF , ' INNER JOIN ', $temp.temp_Schema,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_DSCR_XREF , ' ON ', $temp.temp_Schema ,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF,'.ROWID_XREF = ', $temp.temp_Schema,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_DSCR_XREF , '.PRDCT_MSTR_FK')

'SELECT bo_prdct_mstr_xref1.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS ITEM_SKEY, BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF.LNK_TYP AS LINK_TYPE, bo_prdct_mstr_xref2.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS LINK_SKEY, CASE WHEN BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF.HUB_STATE_IND = ''-1'' THEN ''Y'' ELSE ''N'' END AS HUB_STATE_IND FROM MATERIALS_HUB.C_BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF INNER JOIN MATERIALS_HUB.C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF bo_prdct_mstr_xref1 ON bo_prdct_mstr_xref1.ROWID_XREF = BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF.PRDCT_MSTR_FK_1 INNER JOIN MATERIALS_HUB.C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF bo_prdct_mstr_xref2 ON bo_prdct_mstr_xref2.ROWID_XREF = BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF.PRDCT_MSTR_FK_2'

fn:concat('SELECT C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS ITEM_SKEY, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_UNT AS PACKING_UNIT, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.IAN AS EAN_UPC_NUMBER, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.GRSS_WGHT AS GROSS_WEIGHT, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.NT_WGHT AS NET_WEIGHT, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.UNT_WGHT AS WEIGHT_UNIT_OF_MEASURE, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.VLM AS VOLUME, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.VLM_UNT AS VOLUME_UNIT_OF_MEASURE, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_WDTH AS PCKNG_WDTH, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_HGHT AS PCKNG_HGHT, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_LNGTH AS PCKNG_LNGTH, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_VLM AS PCKNG_VLM, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_UNT_FOR AS PCKNG_UNT_FOR FROM ', $temp.temp_Schema ,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF , ' INNER JOIN ', $temp.temp_Schema,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF , ' ON ', $temp.temp_Schema ,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF,'.ROWID_XREF = ', $temp.temp_Schema,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF , '.PRDCT_MSTR_FK')

(:Agregar Alias al query y formato a la fecha YYYY-MM-DD HHMMSS:) fn:concat('SELECT xref.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS ITEM_SKEY, mstr.MTRL_IDNTFR AS PRODUCT_IDENTIFIER, mstr.OVRLL_MTRL_TYP AS OVERALL_ITEM_TYPE, mstr.MTRL_TYP AS ITEM_TYPE, mstr.CHAMP_CD AS CHAMP_CODE, mstr.PRDCT_CTGR AS PRODUCT_CATEGORY, mstr.TCHNLG_GRP AS TECHNOLOGY_GROUP, mstr.PRDCT_HRCHY AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY, mstr.PRDCT_TYPE AS PRODUCT_TYPE, mstr.BS_UNT_MSR AS BASE_UNIT_OF_MEASURE, mstr.DVSN AS BU, mstr.SBU_DVSN AS SBU, mstr.STATUS_CD AS PRODUCT_STATUS, mstr.ORGNTNG_ID AS ORIGINATING_IDENTIFIER, mstr.SRC_SYSTM_ID AS ORIGINATING_SYSTEM, mstr.NW_PRDCT_LNCH_DT AS NEW_PRODUCT_LAUNCH_DATE, mstr.ITM_EXST_SRC AS ITEM_EXISTS_IN_SOURCE, mstr.CREATOR, to_Char(mstr.CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS') as CREATE_DATE, mstr.UPDATED_BY, to_Char(mstr.LAST_UPDATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS') as LAST_UPDATE_DATE FROM ', $temp.temp_Schema ,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR,' mstr',' INNER JOIN ',$temp.temp_Schema ,'.', $temp.temp_C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF,' xref ON MSTR.ROWID_OBJECT = xref.ROWID_OBJECT AND mstr.SRC_SYSTM_ID = xref.SRC_SYSTM_ID WHERE xref.ROWID_SYSTEM <> 'SYS0'' )
